    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## AI Call Utility Workflow (Optimized)\n\n**Purpose:** Centralized AI inference service utilizing OpenRouter auto-routing and usage tracking.\n\n**Process:**\n1. **Trigger:** Called by other workflows with AI request parameters\n2. **Model Selection:** Routes to Hugging Face (embeddings) or OpenRouter (text)\n3. **Usage Tracking:** Calculates tokens, latency, cost and logs to central analytics workflow\n4. **Response:** Returns AI output with metadata (model used, tokens, latency, cost)\n\n**Input:** `{ prompt, model_preference?, system_message?, max_tokens?, output_format? }`\n**Output:** `{ response, model_used, tokens_input, tokens_output, latency_ms, cost_usd }`",
        "height": 704,
        "width": 2116,
        "color": 6
      },
